[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "陸と空から偵察、完了",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_038_00728",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "大きい建物が１つあっただけで、他は全部\nこんな感じの景色だったわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_023_038_00729",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "建物？　どんな感じのやつ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00730",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "……あんな構造物、今まで見たことがない。\nどう言ったらいいか、難しい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_038_00731",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "そうね、あたしの世界でもちょっと見たことがないわ。\n果ての大陸人のすみかなんじゃない？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_023_038_00732",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "そんな人類がいる？　いや、待てよ……\nもしかしてパルメ族？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00733",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "おや、正解だよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_038_00734",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ちょっと……知ってたなら教えてよね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00735",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "答えというのは自分で考えて、導き出すことに\n意味があると思わないかい？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_038_00736",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "まあ、否定はしないけど……手間とか効率とか\n重視したほうがいい場面もあるでしょ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00737",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "というか、ここがパルメ族のすみかなら\n師匠やザスキアさんもいるんじゃないの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00738",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "またまた正解。\nきっと今頃みんなの到着を待っているはず",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_038_00739",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "あの二人の気配はなかったけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_038_00740",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "あれ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_038_00741",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "ベップちゃんが言うならそうなんでしょうね。\n留守にしているのかしら",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_038_00742",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "シトリン、まだ何か隠してるんじゃないでしょうね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00743",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "いや、これは僕にも予想外。\n……パルメ族にとっても想定外の何かが起こった？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_038_00744",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "まあ、なんにせよ今度は俺たちも探索に参加しよう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_038_00745",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うん。行ってみましょう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00746",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]